<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Who will ascend the mountain of Yahweh?</para>

<para style="q1">Who will stand in his holy place?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />He who has clean hands and a pure heart;</para>

<para style="q1">who has not lifted up a falsehood,</para>

<para style="q1">and has not sworn an oath in order to deceive.</para>
